Benefit of Extend Report
- They ca be integrated with TestNG
- Screenshoot can be captured and displayed for each Step
- They Show the time needed for test execution
- They show

---------------------------
testNG Listener
---------------------------
TC1 -> PASS
TC2 -> FAILED
TC3 -> SKIPPED

Contains the TestNG
Step 1 Create Test Case
Step 2 Create Post Actions (Listener Interface)
Step 3 Create XML File

